'''Estavana Polman''' (born 5 August 1992) is a Dutch [[handball]] player who plays for [[Team Esbjerg]] and the [[Netherlands women's national handball team|Dutch national team]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.estavanapolman.com/persoonlijk.html|title=Persoonlijk|publisher=Estavana Polman official website|accessdate=6 December 2011|language=Dutch|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111128064526/http://www.estavanapolman.com/persoonlijk.html#|archive-date=28 November 2011|dead-url=yes|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.handbal.nl/oranje/nationaal-team-dames/Selectie/|title=Selectie Nationaal Team Dames|language=Dutch|publisher=Nederlands Handbal Verbond|accessdate=18 January 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140210205424/http://www.handbal.nl/oranje/nationaal-team-dames/Selectie/#|archive-date=10 February 2014|dead-url=yes|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://handball.sportresult.com/HBEM14W/PDF/NED-R.pdf|title=2014 European Championship Roster|publisher=[[European Handball Federation|EHF]]|accessdate=7 December 2014}}</ref><ref>[http://www.eurohandball.com/player/538279 EHF profile]</ref>

She represented the Netherlands in younger age categories as well and collected the silver medal at the [[2011 Women's 19 European Handball Championship]]. In addition, she was voted into the all-star team of the tournament in playmaker position.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurohandball.com/article/14116|title=Denmark triumph at Women’s 19 EURO|publisher=European Handball Federation|date=14 August 2011|accessdate=6 December 2011}}</ref>

==Personal life==
As of August 2016, she is in a relationship with Dutch footballer [[Rafael van der Vaart]].<ref>http://www.jv.dk/artikel/2263095:Sport--Her-er-de-saa---turtelduerne-Estavana-Polman-og-Rafael-van-der-Vaart</ref>

On 27 December 2016, they announced that they are expecting a child.<ref>http://hoholok.com/estavana-polman-and-rafael-van-der-vaart-expected-child/</ref>

On 24 June 2017, she gave birth to a 3 kg baby girl, Jesslynn.<ref>https://www.europamester.dk/estavana-polman-har-foedt-lille-prinsesse/</ref>

