'''Stade Am Deich''' is a [[football (soccer)|football]] [[stadium]] in [[Ettelbruck]], in central [[Luxembourg]]. It is currently the home stadium of [[FC Etzella Ettelbruck]]. The stadium has a capacity of about 2,020.
