'''Stade Maniang Soumaré''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Thiès]], [[Senegal]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and serves as a home ground of [[US Rail]]. The stadium holds 8,000 people.

